===[[Season 2]]===
Gelmarr is present when [[Theon Greyjoy]] gives a speech encouraging his crew to resist the Northmen led by [[Ramsay Bolton|Ramsay Snow]] and die a glorious death.&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Valar Morghulis]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;

After handing Theon over, Gelmarr and the other ironborn are [[Flaying|flayed]] alive by [[Ramsay Bolton|Ramsay Snow]] and the soldiers of [[House Bolton]].&lt;ref&gt;&quot;[[Mhysa]]&quot;&lt;/ref&gt;
